cast.overview: A young sex worker from Brooklyn gets her chance at a Cinderella story when she meets and impulsively marries the son of an oligarch. Once the news reaches Russia, her fairytale is threatened as his parents set out to get the marriage annulled.
cast.title: Anora

details.biography:
Ivy Wolk (born August 24, 2004) is an American actress and comedian. She is known for her roles as Tellulah on the Freeform series Everything's Gonna Be Okay (2020) and as Crystal in Sean Baker's film Anora (2024). She is also known online for her provocative social media presence on TikTok and Twitter.
